<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Email Verification OTP</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f6f9fc;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2a9d8f;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
      .otp {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        color: #e63946;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Email Verification</h1>
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>We received a request to verify your email for the <b>Job Referral Portal</b>. Please use the OTP below to complete your verification:</p>

      <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>

      <p>This OTP is valid for <b>5 minutes</b>. If you didnâ€™t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} Job Referral Portal. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
